A MERCEDES-Benz G-Wagon went through the most when it crashed, all in the name of love. A man crashed a rented G-Wagon he had reportedly rented to impress a woman. In the video, the red luxury SUV can be seen damaged by the roadside after crashing. According to autoJosh.com, no life was lost from the accident. As the time of filing this report, the identity of the driver was unknown. The video was posted by Instagram user @mac_rainz, saying: “No need for fake life, them no go hear. Now see what he has put himself into.” 